  "sn22.61:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22",
  "sn22.61:2.1": "6. Upayavagga",
  "sn22.61:3.1": "61. Ādittasutta",
  "sn22.61:4.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ.",
  "sn22.61:4.2": "“<span class=\\\"cross\\\" title=\\\"^pi-tv-kd1#197 [Mahākhandhaka/ Uruvelapāṭihāriyakathā] | ^sn35.28#1 [28. Ādittasutta]\\\" id=\\\"note100\\\">*</span> Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, ādittaṃ, vedanā ādittā, saññā ādittā, saṅkhārā ādittā, viññāṇaṃ ādittaṃ.",
  "sn22.61:4.3": "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi …",
  "sn22.61:4.4": "saññāyapi …",
  "sn22.61:4.5": "saṅkhāresupi …",
  "sn22.61:4.6": "viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati.",
  "sn22.61:4.7": "Nibbindaṃ virajjati;",
  "sn22.61:4.8": "virāgā vimuccati.",
  "sn22.61:4.9": "Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti.",
  "sn22.61:4.10": "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti.",
  "sn22.61:5.1": "Navamaṃ."
}